\c 15
\s Okulahlekileyo: Imvu, uhlamvu lwesiliva, lendodana
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusondela kuye bonke\x + 1.66. 4.22,36. 6.19. 7.29. 11.50.\x* abathelisi lezoni, ukumuzwa\x + Mat. 18.17.\x*.
\v 2 AbaFarisi lababhali basebesola besithi: Lo wemukela izoni, adle lazo\x + 19.7. Mat. 9.10,11. 11.19. Luka 5.30. 7.39.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Wasebatshela lumfanekiso, esithi:
\v 4 Nguwuphi umuntu kini ongathi elezimvu ezilikhulu\x + Mat. 18.12-14.\x*, abeselahlekelwa ngenye yazo, ongazitshiyi ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye\x + Hez. 34.6.\x* egangeni\x + Eks. 3.1. 1 Sam. 17.28.\x*, alandele elahlekileyo, aze ayithole\x + Hez. 34.11,12,16.\x*?
\v 5 Njalo athi ese\add yi\add*tholile a\add ye\add*tshate ethokoza\x + Isa. 40.11.\x*.
\v 6 Esefikile ekhaya, abizele ndawonye abangane labomakhelwane, esithi kubo: Thokozani lami, ngoba ngithole imvu yami ebilahlekile\x + Mat. 9.36.\x*.
\v 7 Ngithi kini: Ngokunjalo kuzakuba khona intokozo ezulwini ngesoni esisodwa esiphendukayo, kulabalungileyo abangamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lasificamunwemunye, abangasweli ukuphenduka\x + Mat. 9.13. Luka 5.32. 15.25.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Loba nguwuphi umfazi othi elenhlamvu zesiliva ezilitshumi, uba elahlekelwa luhlamvu olulodwa lwesiliva, angalumathisi isibane, athanyele indlu, adingisise aze a\add lu\add*thole?
\v 9 Njalo nxa ese\add lu\add*tholile ubizela ndawonye abangane labomakhelwane, athi: Thokozani lami, ngoba sengilutholile uhlamvu lwesiliva ebengilahlekelwe yilo.
\v 10 Ngokunjalo, ngithi kini, ikhona intokozo phambi kwezingilosi zikaNkulunkulu ngesoni esisodwa esiphendukayo\x + Mat. 18.10.\x*.
\p
\v 11 Wasesithi: Umuntu othile wayelamadodana amabili;
\v 12 encinyane yawo yasisithi kuyise: Baba, nginika isabelo sempahla\x + Dute. 21.17.\x* esiqondene \add lami\add*. Wasewehlukanisela impahla\x + Mark. 12.44.\x*.
\v 13 Njalo kungelansuku ezinengi emva kwalokhu indodana encinyane yabutha konke yasuka yahamba yaya elizweni elikhatshana\x + Mat. 21.33.\x*, njalo lapho yachitha khona impahla yayo, iphila okobuhlanya.
\v 14 Yathi isichithile konke, kwavela indlala enkulu kulelolizwe, yona yasiqala ukuswela.
\v 15 Yasisuka yazihlanganisa lesinye sezakhamizi zalelolizwe; njalo sayithuma emasimini aso ukuze yeluse izingulube.
\v 16 Yasifisa ukugcwalisa isisu sayo ngamakhasi ingulube eziwadlayo; njalo kwakungelamuntu oyinika \add ulutho\x + 16.21.\x*\add*.
\v 17 Kwathi \add ingqondo\add* yayo isibuyile yathi\x + Seb. 12.11.\x*: Zingaki izisebenzi zikababa eziqhatshiweyo ezilezinkwa ezinengi kakhulu, kanti mina ngiyafa yindlala;
\v 18 ngizasukuma ngiye kubaba, ngithi kuye: Baba, ngonile ezulwini, laphambi kwakho\x + 15.21.\x*;
\v 19 njalo\x + 15.21.\x* kangisafanelanga ukubizwa ngithiwe \add ngiy\add*indodana yakho\x + 7.6.\x*; ngenza ngibe njengomunye wezisebenzi zakho eziqhatshiweyo.
\v 20 Yasisukuma yaya kuyise. Kodwa kuthe isesekhatshana, uyise wayibona, waba lesihelo\x + Seb. 2.39.\x*, wagijima\x + Jak. 4.8.\x* wawela entanyeni yayo\x + Gen. 45.14. 46.29. Seb. 20.37.\x*, wayanga\x + 2 Sam. 14.33.\x*.
\v 21 Indodana yasisithi kuye: Baba, ngonile ezulwini\x + Jobe 33.27.\x* laphambi kwakho\x + Hlab. 51.4.\x*, futhi kangisafanelanga ukubizwa \add ngokuthi\add* \add ngiy\add*indodana yakho\x + 7.6.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uyise wathi ezincekwini zakhe: Khuphani lilethe isembatho esihle kakhulu liyigqokise\x + Zek. 3.4.\x*, lifake indandatho esandleni sayo\x + Gen. 41.42.\x*, lamanyathela enyaweni \add zayo\x + Hez. 16.10. Mat. 10.10. Luka 22.35. Mark. 6.9.\x*\add*;
\v 23 lilethe ithole elinonisiweyo\x + 15.27,30. Mat. 22.4.\x* li\add li\add*hlabe, njalo sidle\x + Gen. 31.54.\x* sithokoze\x + 15.24,29,32. 12.19. 16.19.\x*;
\v 24 ngoba indodana yami le ibifile, isibuye yaphila; ibilahlekile, itholiwe\x + 15.32. Efe. 2.1,5. 5.14. Kol. 2.13. Isam. 3.1.\x*; basebeqala ukuthokoza\x + 15.24,29,32. 12.19. 16.19.\x*.
\v 25 Kodwa indodana yakhe endala yayisensimini; yathi isiza isondela endlini, yezwa ukuhlabelela lokusina\x + Dan. 3.5,10,15.\x*.
\v 26 Yasibizela kuyo omunye wezinceku, yabuza ukuthi zitshoni lezizinto\x + 18.36.\x*.
\v 27 Yasisithi kuyo: Umfowenu ufikile; loyihlo uhlabile ithole elinonisiweyo, ngoba ememukele ephila\x + 15.27,30. Mat. 22.4.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa yathukuthela, ayizange ifune ukungena; ngakho uyise waphuma wayincenga.
\v 29 Kodwa yaphendula yathi kuyise: Khangela, iminyaka engaka ngikusebenzela, kangizange ngeqe umlayo wakho, kodwa kawuzange unginike lazinyane lembuzi\x + Levi 4.13,14,22,23.\x*, ukuze ngijabule kanye labangane bami\x + 15.24,29,32. 12.19. 16.19.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa kuthe isifikile lindodana yakho eyachitha impahla yakho lezifebe, wayihlabela\x + 15.27,30. Mat. 22.4.\x* ithole elinonisiweyo\x + Levi 4.13,14,22,23.\x*.
\v 31 Wasesithi kuyo: Ndodana, wena uhlezi ulami\x + Joha. 8.35.\x*, futhi konke okungokwami kungokwakho\x + 15.12.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa bekufanele ukujabula lokuthokoza\x + 15.24,29,32. 12.19. 16.19.\x*; ngoba umfowenu lo owayefile, usebuye waphila; wayelahlekile, utholiwe\x + 15.24.\x*.
